abstract: In The New York Times TV Ratings Game, 12.3 percent of the participants correctly predicted "The Playboy Club" on NBC would be canceled after three episodes.
snippet: In The New York Times TV Ratings Game, 12.3 percent of the participants correctly predicted "The Playboy Club" on NBC would be canceled after three episodes.
lead_paragraph: The first casualty of the new television season, "The Playboy Club," which was canceled by NBC on Tuesday, was also one of the shows considered least likely to make it this season, according to players in The New York Times TV Ratings Game. And 12.3 percent of the participating readers correctly predicted that show would last only three episodes.
